text: Ribeirinha is a parish in the district of Ribeira Grande in the Azores. The population in 2011 was 2,349,Instituto Nacional de Estatística in an area of 17.98 km².Eurostat It contains the localities Gramas, Lameiro, Ribeirinha, Santa Rosa and Santo António. ==References== Category:Parishes of Ribeira Grande, Azores
title: Ribeirinha (Ribeira Grande)
